metadata.name: RaveFaces - Rave Rhymes
metadata.description: This collection features 500 unique cards, each with an AI-generated rhyme about rave culture. The RaveFaces artists on the second Ritual prompted ChatGPT to create these rhymes. The symbols on the cards has a role in the game. Stake your NFT in the DAPP at RaveFaces.com, to earn $R4V3 token rewards daily, and collect more rave music NFTs.

attributes.value: Electronic music from an AI mind, technologically advanced and refined.
please give me 4 rhymes, maximum 128 character, about an AI who made better techno than any real person
